<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000845/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Progressive assessment
Evaluation activity Modality Weight
Attendance and participation Individual 10%
Group assignment and work presentation belonging to the first part of the subject Group 40%
Group assignment and work presentation belonging to the second part of the subject Group 40%
BDLab Redthread modules Individual 10%

Global assessment test and Extraordinary assessment test
Evaluation activity Modality Weight
Assessment test (evaluation of the content belonging to the first and second part of the subject) individual 80%

